  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dbd\u0db4\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dba \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0db1 \u0d85\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dba\u0da7 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 21\u0daf\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel to vehicle number with license from 21st",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Kumara Rajapaksa, Chairman of the Petrol Station Owners Association, said in a press conference held in Colombo today (19th) that fuel will be issued with the 'National Fuel Licence' only according to the last digit of the vehicle's registration number from tomorrow (21st)."
      ],
